PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT ?uri
WHERE {
  wd:Q1336200 wdt:P112 ?uri # Using the first entity for Penguin Books
  # Or, alternatively, if we are unsure which entity is correct or if we want to query all entities for Penguin Books:
  # UNION wd:Q3374730 wdt:P112 ?uri
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?label
WHERE {
  ?x wdt:P175 wd:Q303.
  ?x wdt:P264 ?label.
  ?x wdt:P577 ?y.
  BIND (STR(?y) AS ?releaseDate)
  FILTER (lang(?label) = 'en')
}
ORDER BY ASC(?releaseDate)
OFFSET 0
LIMIT 1

          strstarts(?instrument, "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q8338")).
  FILTER (strstarts(?occupation, "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5280538") ||
          strstarts(?occupation, "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q806349")).
}
